Description: Dooney & Bourke Embossed Pebble Leather Shelby Shopper , You think Santa has an impressive bag? Check out the Shelby shopper from Dooney & Bourke--this is the "it" bag you just have to have this season! The newest look in luxury, this bag features Dooney & Bourke's Clairmont leather--a lightweight leather with a delicate embossed texture. And the elegant exterior is highlighted by goldtone hardware, butterscotch-colored vachetta leather trim, and a new brand logo. The sophisticated design continues as you look inside. There's plenty of storage and handy pockets all gorgeously framed by Dooney's new neutral chevron lining. The coordinating wristlet and key fob can be tossed into the shopper, or grab them and go when you only need the basics.
